both on the hill and in the valley, too. I mean,

11:28.035 --> 11:32.179
there was a tremendous outbreak of cotton all over 
the country along about World War I days when they

11:33.543 --> 11:43.055
were seeking the cellulose of cotton to make 
gunpowder. And this continued until about 1925

11:43.075 --> 12:02.318
when there was a combination of a market crash and a 
