23:08.232 --> 23:18.145
took a copy of the Supreme Court opinion that Brown 
v. School Board distributed to my fellow members.

23:18.901 --> 23:47.642
told him i said i mean there was a lot of talk at that 
time it's not going to be i mean over the south they

23:18.901 --> 23:47.642
were saying well we're not going to do it and all 
like that i told him i said forget about it it's here

23:18.901 --> 23:47.642
it has already happened there's no arguing with it 
so we ought to get with it and we started attempting

23:18.901 --> 23:47.642
to identify at that time black students in the 
black system that could, without any difficulty

23:48.061 --> 24:08.992
