people have always been able to borrow money in

24:18.385 --> 24:24.973
this community. That's something that very few 
people know about. I don't ever remember a time

24:28.437 --> 24:35.847
that a responsible black individual couldn't 
obtain bank credit, the very best credit. He

24:35.867 --> 24:41.033
didn't have to go to a backstreet shyster loan 
company. He could go talk to the chief loan officer

24:41.053 --> 24:46.640
of any bank in this community. I've seen it happen 
many, many times. I know that I have waited in line

24:50.363 --> 25:04.175
