25:21.599 --> 25:49.767
Delaney the two vice presidents and the main loan 
officers of the bank sat right there immediately

25:21.599 --> 25:49.767
visible to everyone behind a rail and the 
customary practice and everybody did it was to go

25:21.599 --> 25:49.767
